 ### Crear incidente
POST http://localhost:8080/incidents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Database connection timeout",
  "description": "Production database not responding",
  "severity": "P1",
  "assignedTo": "ops-team"
}

###

### Listar todos los incidentes
GET http://localhost:8080/incidents

###

### Obtener incidente por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/incidents/{{incidentId}}

###

### Acknowledge incidente
PATCH http://localhost:8080/incidents/{{incidentId}}/acknowledge

###

### Resolver incidente
PATCH http://localhost:8080/incidents/{{incidentId}}/resolve

###

### Eliminar incidente (solo si está RESOLVED)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/incidents/{{incidentId}}

###

### Stream SSE (abrir en navegador o usar curl)
GET http://localhost:8080/incidents/stream

###
